<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Eased Tech Solutions</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Cloud Consulting, DevOps, AWS, and Automation Solutions">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #1e3a8a;
      --accent: #3b82f6;
      --light: #f9fafb;
      --dark: #1f2937;
      --font: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: var(--font); background: white; color: var(--dark); line-height: 1.6; }
    header { background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--accent)); color: white; padding: 5rem 1rem; text-align: center; }
    header h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
    header p { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; background: white; color: var(--primary); border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
    section { padding: 4rem 1rem; }
    .container { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .features, .testimonials { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
    .card { background: var(--light); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    h2 { font-size: 2rem; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center; }
    footer { background: var(--light); text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; }
    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Eased Tech Solutions</h1>
    <p>Expert Cloud, DevOps & Automation Services</p>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn">Book a Free Consultation</a>
  </header>

  <section id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Cloud Consulting</h3>
          <p>Design, migration, and optimization across AWS & Azure cloud platforms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>DevOps</h3>
          <p>Infrastructure as Code, CI/CD pipelines, and secure automation practices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>AWS Architecture</h3>
          <p>Scalable, cost-efficient, and well-architected solutions with best practices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Automation</h3>
          <p>Scripted deployments, provisioning, monitoring, and self-healing systems.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="trust">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Secure & Reliable</h2>
      <p style="text-align:center">We follow industry standards and best practices for performance, cost efficiency, and compliance (SOC 2 Ready).</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Clients Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonials">
        <div class="card">
          <p>“Eased Tech transformed our AWS setup — fast, responsive, and secure.”</p>
          <p><strong>– Placeholder Corp</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p>“Their DevOps automation saved us 40+ hours monthly. Highly recommended.”</p>
          <p><strong>– Sample Startup</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p style="text-align:center">Reach out at <a href="mailto:info@eased.ca">info@eased.ca</a><br>or message us on Fiverr / Upwork (links coming soon).</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Eased Tech Solutions — All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
